            <span class="utterance" who="#brinI" start="198.829" end="x">What I thought of Rumkowski? Rumkowski was very . . . a leader of the German powers. Everything had to be exact. Everything that he got from Amtsleiter Biebow.<note n="2"><span class="note">Hans Biebow (1902-1947) was the head of Nazi administration of the Łódź Ghetto.</span><sup><a href="#note_2">2</a></sup></note> He with the help of his police carried out precisely. [unintelligible]. He was a very strong person, huge. [unintelligible]. If someone were caught stealing a potato, one went [unintelligible]. Sent to <a class="placename" href="#vothC4" type="camp">Auschwitz</a> [unintelligible].</span>
